you probably see this sense of urgency , a little bit scared , but also external concentrations , a really hard problem to solve .
if you play , you &apos;ll see some nuances here that are zoomed up , and the mouth is a sign of optimism . the eyebrows are a surprise .
this is a player standing on the edge of what &apos;s called an epan victory .
oh , you know that . ok . prima . so we have some players here .
one epic victory is a result so overwhelmingly positive that they didn &apos;t know earlier that it was possible at all .
it was almost beyond the imagination .
and when they do it , they &apos;re shocked that they &apos;re actually capable of something like this . this is an epic victory .
this player is standing in front of an epic victory .
and this is what we need to see on millions of faces of problem-solvers around the world when we tackle the barriers of the next century , the face of those standing against all the odds on the edge of an epic victory .
well , unfortunately , we &apos;re more likely to see this face in real life when we face difficult problems .
