of course , the problem is that , as we start to look at all the similarities , we have to start asking about why we sustain certain divisions .
well , remember , i want to sustain certain separations , anatomically speaking , in our culture .
i don &apos;t want to give a fish the same rights as a human .
i don &apos;t want to say that we should be taking away from anatomy .
