you can see here , he &apos;s beginning to roll , and the boat &apos;s moved to the other side , the man &apos;s standing there .
this is the average size of a greenland iceberg .
it &apos;s about 120 feet out of the water , or 40 meters .
and this video is real time .
and just like this , the iceberg shows you a different side of its personality .
