we lose them .
go from the very few choices to the very many , then stay there .
they &apos;re the same information . it &apos;s the same number of possibilities .
the only thing i &apos;ve done is to change the order in which this information is presented .
when i start with the simple beginning , i learn how to choose .
even though the gear chooses nothing to tell me about my preferences in interior equipment , it still prepare me to choose .
