it says , &quot; this airplane is made up of hundreds of thousands of pieces that work together to make your flight safer . &apos; doesn &apos;t you make it more confident ? &quot;
we know that an developmental process is not optimal when it becomes too complicated .
so we &apos;re starting to rely on computers for a process that &apos;s very different from classical engineering .
it allows us to produce things with a much higher complexity than the normal methods would allow us to produce .
and yet , we don &apos;t quite understand the possibilities of this yet .
so , in a way , we overwhelm technology .
we &apos;re now using these programs to make computers much faster , so that we &apos;re able to do these processes even faster .
